  "detailed_description": "Once upon a time, there was a cruel clan that ruled over the area called FeiYangDian.<br>The leader and his thugs killing those who are against him and taking everything wealth, bring lawlessness and chaos to the people.<br>The world needs a hero to end this evilness.<br><br>WuJiDaoRen specially designed this physics-based character locomotion system, that generates real time fighting and reaction animations.<br>Through the interactive moves and fluid combat motion, and tried to present the beauty of Chinese Martial Arts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/29f1a3441417f9f5ef9c9674b146ab30.poster.avif?t=1745569046\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/29f1a3441417f9f5ef9c9674b146ab30.webm?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/29f1a3441417f9f5ef9c9674b146ab30.mp4?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Character will move like in the real world, the move and the balance is calculated by steps and the force used.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/54f0ca4c1ffa69b0cb29abad39e93ce6.poster.avif?t=1745569046\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/54f0ca4c1ffa69b0cb29abad39e93ce6.webm?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/54f0ca4c1ffa69b0cb29abad39e93ce6.mp4?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each action move is simulated by physics, calculates its speed, momenten, the balance state, where it hits and how it hits.<br>Moves can intersect with each other like in the real world. The character can be dragged, pushed, and tripped, and will behave like what it should be.<br>Every combat result is unique. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/c46ab730d506b9ee6c52c0ba16138b67.poster.avif?t=1745569046\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/c46ab730d506b9ee6c52c0ba16138b67.webm?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/c46ab730d506b9ee6c52c0ba16138b67.mp4?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/d8808ae97d4c8b1ce5c3aa007d40b3a1.poster.avif?t=1745569046\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/d8808ae97d4c8b1ce5c3aa007d40b3a1.webm?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/d8808ae97d4c8b1ce5c3aa007d40b3a1.mp4?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>There also have various weapons that can be chosen. Each type of weapon brings a different fighting style and feel.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/8978a4bb99f22df09d2bed47c3b0bb48.poster.avif?t=1745569046\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/8978a4bb99f22df09d2bed47c3b0bb48.webm?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/8978a4bb99f22df09d2bed47c3b0bb48.mp4?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Once upon a time, there was a cruel clan that ruled over the area called FeiYangDian.<br>The leader and his thugs killing those who are against him and taking everything wealth, bring lawlessness and chaos to the people.<br>The world needs a hero to end this evilness.<br><br>WuJiDaoRen specially designed this physics-based character locomotion system, that generates real time fighting and reaction animations.<br>Through the interactive moves and fluid combat motion, and tried to present the beauty of Chinese Martial Arts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/29f1a3441417f9f5ef9c9674b146ab30.poster.avif?t=1745569046\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/29f1a3441417f9f5ef9c9674b146ab30.webm?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/29f1a3441417f9f5ef9c9674b146ab30.mp4?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Character will move like in the real world, the move and the balance is calculated by steps and the force used.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/54f0ca4c1ffa69b0cb29abad39e93ce6.poster.avif?t=1745569046\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/54f0ca4c1ffa69b0cb29abad39e93ce6.webm?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/54f0ca4c1ffa69b0cb29abad39e93ce6.mp4?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each action move is simulated by physics, calculates its speed, momenten, the balance state, where it hits and how it hits.<br>Moves can intersect with each other like in the real world. The character can be dragged, pushed, and tripped, and will behave like what it should be.<br>Every combat result is unique. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/c46ab730d506b9ee6c52c0ba16138b67.poster.avif?t=1745569046\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/c46ab730d506b9ee6c52c0ba16138b67.webm?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/c46ab730d506b9ee6c52c0ba16138b67.mp4?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/d8808ae97d4c8b1ce5c3aa007d40b3a1.poster.avif?t=1745569046\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/d8808ae97d4c8b1ce5c3aa007d40b3a1.webm?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/d8808ae97d4c8b1ce5c3aa007d40b3a1.mp4?t=1745569046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>There also have various weapons that can be chosen. Each type of weapon brings a different fighting style and feel.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/8978a4bb99f22df09d2bed47c3b0bb48.poster.avif?t=1745569046\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211120/extras/8978a4bb99f22df09d2bed